comments: Middleton (MIL) avoids initiating any illegal contact with Thomas (BKN), but Lopez (MIL) initiates contact to his head during the driving shot attempt.
Portis (MIL) turns to roll and marginal contact occurs with Watanabe (BKN) after the hand-off.
Watanabe (BKN) is not in a legal guarding position and extends his arms forward, initiating contact to Portis's (MIL) arm and affecting his shot attempt.
Sharpe (BKN) establishes himself in Portis' (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Lopez (MIL) brings his hands toward Duke Jr. (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as Lopez releases away to roll.
Middleton (MIL) slides his pivot foot prior to releasing his post shot attempt.
Sharpe (BKN) cleanly deflects the pass and steals the ball.
Middleton (MIL) brings his forearm slightly forward and marginal body contact occurs with Thomas (BKN) during his driving shot attempt.
Sharpe (BKN) reaches for the rebound and marginal arm contact occurs with Lopez (MIL) that does not affect his ability to tip the ball in.
Lopez (MIL) cleanly blocks the shot attempt before it touches the backboard.
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on Allen (MIL).
Allen (MIL) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Thomas' (BKN) arm.
Sharpe (BKN) brings his arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Lopez's (MIL) arm as both players pursue the rebound.
